trans-unit.source: Consists of a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" /> objects to be used with catalogs of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> controls.
trans-unit.target: Se compone de una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" /> que se van a utilizar con catálogos de controles <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" />.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Esta clase no puede heredarse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> class is created by the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in their implementations of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> se crea una clase por los distintos <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controles en sus implementaciones de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: For each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control that is contained in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control, a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object is created.
trans-unit.target: Para cada <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control que se encuentra en un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> (control), un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> se crea el objeto.

trans-unit.source: This object maintains basic information about a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, including its ID, its title, its description, and a path to an associated icon.
trans-unit.target: Este objeto mantiene información básica sobre un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, incluida su identificador, su título, su descripción y una ruta de acceso a un icono asociado.

trans-unit.source: The various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls can use a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to display a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control's information in the catalog, without having to create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control itself.
trans-unit.target: Los distintos <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controles pueden utilizar un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objeto que se va a mostrar un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> información del control en el catálogo, sin tener que crear una instancia de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> propio control.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> class is used internally by the Web Parts control set to maintain a collection of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects used in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> clase se utiliza internamente por el control de elementos Web establecido para mantener una colección de todos los <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objetos que se usan en un catálogo.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> collection is used only when a page is in catalog display mode.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> colección solo se usa cuando una página está en modo de presentación de catálogo.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control is being rendered, it loops through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> collection, adding the information from each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to the displayed catalog.
trans-unit.target: Cuando un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control que se va a representar, recorre en bucle la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> colección, agregar la información de cada uno <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objeto al catálogo mostrado.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia vacía de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: This overload of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A> constructor can be used to create an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Esta sobrecarga de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A> constructor puede utilizarse para crear una colección vacía.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> control creates an empty <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> object if the content of an imported description file is `null`.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> control crea vacío <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> objeto si el contenido de un archivo de descripción importado es `null`.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" /> objects that correspond to the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> controls in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: Una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" /> que se corresponden con los controles <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> de un catálogo.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" /> object by passing in an <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de un objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" /> transfiriendo una colección <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29> constructor is used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method implementations within the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls to create a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29> constructor se usa por la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> implementaciones del método dentro de los distintos <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controles para crear una colección de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objetos.

trans-unit.target: Un valor booleano que indica si existe un determinado objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" /> en una colección <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.Contains%2A> method enables you to determine whether a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object is part of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.Contains%2A> método le permite determinar si un determinado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objeto forma parte de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> colección.

trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.CopyTo%2A> método resulta útil cuando desea ensamblar una matriz personalizada que puede contener el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objetos en el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> colección.

trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.Item%2A> indexer le permite tener acceso a un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objeto en un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> colección según un identificador único.
